22:32.520 --> 22:35.205
-(LAUGHS)
- That's a loaded fucking weapon.

22:35.280 --> 22:39.001
We could fuck by the fire with the maids
standing to attention and watching.

22:39.080 --> 22:40.127
What can they do?

22:40.200 --> 22:41.326
- Give it here.
- Nothing.

22:41.400 --> 22:43.846
There are no rules for you. Hmm?

22:43.920 --> 22:45.001
Give me the fucking gun.

22:45.080 --> 22:47.606
You have maids here.
You can bring a maid into the room.

22:47.680 --> 22:49.648
