23:01.200 --> 23:02.725
I can be an actress.

23:03.480 --> 23:05.084
Who do you want me to be?

23:06.080 --> 23:07.161
Your dead wife?

23:07.240 --> 23:08.810
Now, that's enough.
Give me the fucking gun!

23:08.880 --> 23:12.043
If you don't like something,
you say stop, and it stops. Hmm?

23:12.800 --> 23:14.564
But you are afraid of it.

23:14.640 --> 23:17.246
You break the law,
but you obey the rules. Why?

23:18.520 --> 23:21.285
Did you know that madness sets you free?

23:21.360 --> 23:23.761
Otherwise, we're just peasants
obeying the law.

23:26.160 --> 23:29.403
There is madness inside your head, too.
I can see that.

23:30.520 --> 23:32.522
Let a duchess show you something.

23:33.240 --> 23:34.685
